<p>
  SteamVents is a place to air out your thoughts, and get help without pressure. We have resources gathered in one location and include Instawell&trade;, a pay for application for mental health, easy accessible at the bottom left of every page.
 </p>
<p>
  SteamVents is completely free to use and will continue to add features as time goes on. Some features already included are:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    Venting: where you can let out steam and your air your thoughts. </li>
    <li>Article search for health topics.</li>
    <li>Websites and phone numbers for treatment.</li>
    <li>Access to Instawell.</li>
  </ul>

      <p>SteamVents was created with Ruby on Rails by Bemilton Suero. It was inspired by my own struggles along with the observation of the struggles of my peers around me. You can find my information on <a href="https://github.com/bemsuero">GitHub</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bemilton-suero/">LinkedIn</a> and if you would like to support more projects like this: <a href="https://ko-fi.com/milesmorales">Ko-Fi</a></p>
